# Dev fixture secrets for the credential-proxy local_dev SecretStore
# (Stream I.1b). Mounted into the credential-proxy container and read via
# EXPERT_WORK_CRED_PROXY_SECRET_STORE_ENV_FILE.
#
# Placeholder values only — NOT real credentials (same status as the dev
# DB password in docker-compose.yml). Consumed by the #60 egress e2e:
# the sandbox sends X-Expert-Work-Secret-Ref: e2e-upstream-token and the proxy
# injects this value as `Authorization: Bearer ...` toward mock-upstream.
e2e-upstream-token=dev-e2e-upstream-token-not-a-real-secret
